      <p>Using Bayesâ theorem and Eqs. 1, this inequality becomes <italic>Ïµ</italic><sup><italic>d</italic></sup>(1 â <italic>f</italic> )â<italic>&lt;</italic>â(1 â <italic>Ïµ</italic>)<sup><italic>d</italic></sup><italic>f</italic>, or</p>
