      </p>
      <p>The expected value of <italic>X</italic><sub><italic>ib</italic></sub> is E(<italic>X</italic><sub><italic>ib</italic></sub>)â=â<italic>n</italic><sub><italic>ib</italic></sub><italic>Î¼</italic><sub><italic>i</italic></sub>, and <italic>Ï</italic> is a dispersion parameter, defined such that</p>
      <p>
        <disp-formula id="bmcM5">
          <label>(5)</label>
          <mml:math id="M5" name="1471-2164-14-501-i5" overflow="scroll">
            <mml:mrow>
              <mml:mi mathvariant="normal">Var</mml:mi>
              <mml:mfenced open="(" close=")">
                <mml:msub>
                  <mml:mi>X</mml:mi>
                  <mml:mi mathvariant="italic">ib</mml:mi>
                </mml:msub>
              </mml:mfenced>
              <mml:mo>=</mml:mo>
              <mml:msub>
                <mml:mi>n</mml:mi>
                <mml:mi mathvariant="italic">ib</mml:mi>
              </mml:msub>
              <mml:msub>
                <mml:mi>Î¼</mml:mi>
                <mml:mi>i</mml:mi>
              </mml:msub>
              <mml:mfenced open="(" close=")">
                <mml:mrow>
                  <mml:mn>1</mml:mn>
                  <mml:mo>â</mml:mo>
